dmca.title: Chinese travel site complains of copying
dmca.body:
Dear Google Editor, 

Hereunder, I, on behalf of www.chinadiscover.net and www.sinowaytravel.com, the property of Guilin . Scenery Internatinal Travel Service Co. Ltd., would like to notify you a copyright infringement with part of our website content.
The website of the plagiary is: http://www.yunnantravel.cn, and the plagiary copy everything from http://www.chinadiscover.net/, you might kindly check the page of reservation and the title is still mentioned " Reserve Form
dmca.principal_name: Guilin . Scenery Internatinal Travel Service Co. Ltd.
